---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base 
  title="About the Author - Duy Thanh" 
  description="Learn about Duy Thanh, the creator behind GPT Breeze, the privacy-focused AI Chrome extension that helps you save time with AI-powered productivity shortcuts."
>
  <style>
    .author-hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 48px 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, theme('colors.accent-blue-light') 0%, theme('colors.ui-surface') 100%);
      border-radius: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
    
    .author-avatar {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      background-image: url('/duythanh.png');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      border: 3px solid theme('colors.accent-blue');
    }
    
    .author-content {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    
    .author-content h2 {
      color: theme('colors.brand-fg');
      margin: 32px 0 16px;
    }
    
    .author-content p {
      color: theme('colors.brand-muted');
      margin: 16px 0;
    }
    
    .expertise-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      margin: 32px 0;
    }
    
    .expertise-item {
      background: theme('colors.ui-surface');
      border: 1px solid theme('colors.ui-border');
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    .expertise-item h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      color: theme('colors.brand-fg');
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    
    .expertise-item p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: theme('colors.brand-muted');
    }
    
    .contact-links {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 24px;
      margin: 48px 0;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    
    .contact-links a {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background: theme('colors.ui-surface');
      border: 1px solid theme('colors.ui-border');
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: theme('colors.brand-fg');
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }
    
    .contact-links a:hover {
      background: theme('colors.accent-blue-light');
      border-color: theme('colors.accent-blue');
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .author-hero {
        padding: 32px 20px;
      }
      
      .author-avatar {
        width: 100px;
        height: 100px;
        font-size: 40px;
      }
      
      .contact-links {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <article class="author-content">
    <div class="author-hero">
      <div class="author-avatar"></div>
      <h1>Duy Thanh</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin: 0;">Product gal ‚ö°Ô∏è indie maker ‚ö°Ô∏è Building GPT Breeze</p>
    </div>

    <div class="author-content">
      <h2>My Mission</h2>
      <p>
        I'm passionate about making AI accessible, affordable, and privacy-focused. 
        GPT Breeze was born out of my frustration with expensive subscription models and privacy concerns 
        surrounding AI productivity tools.
      </p>

      <p>
        My philosophy is simple: you should own your data, control your costs, and have the freedom 
        to choose which AI models work best for your needs. That's why I built GPT Breeze with a 
        BYOM (Bring Your Own Model) approach.
      </p>

      <h2>What I Bring to the Table</h2>
      <div class="expertise-list">
        <div class="expertise-item">
          <h3>üîí Privacy First</h3>
          <p>Your data goes directly to your chosen AI provider. I don't store conversations or personal information.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="expertise-item">
          <h3>üí° User-Centric Design</h3>
          <p>Every feature is designed based on real user feedback and productivity needs.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="expertise-item">
          <h3>‚ö° Performance Focus</h3>
          <p>Lightweight extension that doesn't slow down your browsing experience.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="expertise-item">
          <h3>üõ†Ô∏è Technical Excellence</h3>
          <p>Clean code, secure architecture, and continuous improvement based on user needs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>My Story</h2>
      <p>
        Like many professionals, I found myself paying $20+ monthly subscriptions for AI tools 
        I only used occasionally. I wanted something simple: a browser extension that could 
        summarize content, help with writing, and save time - without the privacy concerns or 
        subscription fatigue.
      </p>

      <p>
        After trying various solutions and finding them lacking, I decided to build my own. 
        GPT Breeze represents my vision of what AI productivity tools should be: transparent, 
        affordable, and respectful of user privacy.
      </p>

      <h2>Looking Forward</h2>
      <p>
        I'm continuously working to improve GPT Breeze based on user feedback. My roadmap includes 
        more AI provider integrations, enhanced productivity features, and better local AI support.
      </p>

      <p>
        I believe the future of AI tools is user-controlled, privacy-focused, and built around 
        genuine value rather than subscription lock-in.
      </p>

